sen uniformly at random. We also present\ncorollaries of the theorem for the preferential attachment model, and study\ngeneralizations with household (or motif) structure. The latter was only known\nfor the configuration model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 01:09:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-19"}
