n electrostatic field leads to the finite. In this\ncourse are derived the modified version of Coulomb potential and of radiation\nreaction without renormalization which contains an interference effect (a\nnonlinear effect that does not obey LSP).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 03:53:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-20"}
