iency (SE) and energy efficiency (EE) than traditional\nMU-MIMO systems can be achieved. Both mathematical analysis and simulation\nresults validate that the proposed scheme can effectively eliminate both\ninterferences of the practical downlink MU-OAM channel and approaches the\nperformance of the ideal MU-OAM channel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 09:21:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-19"}
