mising material to exhibit novel topological superconducting phases, but\nalso the rather large energy dispersion of type-II nodal lines in this\nconfiguration, may offer a distinguished platform for realization of novel\ntopological features in two-dimensional limit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 09:42:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-19"}
