ubbles' buoyancy power can efficiently\noffset the radiative cooling of the intragroup medium. However, the bubbles\nhave still not thoroughly mixed with the thermal gas, after hundreds of million\nyears, likely under the action of magnetic fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 11:08:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-22"}
