ts demonstrate that\nthe proposed design significantly improves the OFDM rate performance as well as\nthe RIS's adaptability to wideband signals compared to baseline schemes without\nemploying DAM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 13:33:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-19"}
