 with different implementations of the same\nmodels provides an important insight into the role of radiative energy loss as\nwell as charm quark recombination in the hadronisation mechanisms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 15:49:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Nov 2021 09:12:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 9 Mar 2022 10:38:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-10"}
