 liquid flow rates, the spatial integration of\nlocal liquid fluxes represents 92 to 99% of the injected liquid flow rate.\nThese good results demonstrate that the Doppler probe provides reliable\nstatistics on drops velocity and size.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Oct 2021 14:00:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-26"}
